{
  "title": "TiledObject",
  "description": "A parsed Tiled object, placed in an TiledObjectLayer or a tile's collision `objectgroup`. The shape of the object is determined by which of point, ellipse, polygon, polyline, text, or gid is set; if none are set, the object is a plain rectangle spanning `[x, y, width, height]`.",
